race.description: Peter Kittle Toyota Para Hills Mixed Stake Pr1 D
race.comment: DARK MOONSHINE (8) has a strong record this track and trip with eight wins and eight placings from 21 starts. In the money last time at this track (22.88) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4 length second. Looks suited here and rates on top. MAJESTIC MCLAREN (5) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (31.57) in a OPEN at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Expected to do much better this time. BUDGEREE (7) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Secret Super (23.34) in a OPEN. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. PRIME OF LIFE (1) can run a bold race on best form.
